description:
It\&amp;#039;s time to dust off those old megamix records and tapes.

This the VERY FIRST MIX from DMC (aka Disco Mix Club), a DJ-only subscription club which has been running for 25 years.
They produce monthly releases, which to start with were only released on cassette tape.
Producing mixes on cassettes has an advantage over vinyl in that longer individual mixes can be recorded, up to the entire length of a tape, which is much longer than what can be fitted onto an LP.
DMC used this advantage with their first mix, DMC Floorfillers Volume 1, which is 45 minutes long.

